notes.p: The model reproduces the calcium oscillation dependent activation-deactivation kinetics of nuclear factor of activated T cells (NFAT) as depicted in Fig 4a of the paper. A simple algorithm in the events section takes care of the calcium oscillation. The model was successfully tested on MathSBML.
